data_table.name: TOPMed_WGS_SAFHS_Subject_Phenotypes
data_table.study_name: NHLBI TOPMed: San Antonio Family Heart Study (SAFHS)
data_table.description: This subject phenotype data table includes sex, ethnicity, age, anthropometric measurements (n=4 variables; height, weight, BMI, waist circumference), type 2 diabetes status and age of diagnosis, systolic and diastolic blood pressure measurements, blood measurements (n=7 variables; cholesterol, triglycerides, HDL, fasting and 2 hour glucose, fasting and 2 hour insulin), smoking status, medications (n=3 variables; diabetes, BP, lipids), and cardiovascular disease (CVD) status.
